Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,---- Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.52,0:00:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make it a little more lively...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.90,0:00:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.86,0:00:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should raise the tempo a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.44,0:00:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.78,0:00:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The drums drive the beat,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.99,0:00:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the melody pumps me up,\Nand the words flow out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The moment when I find that\N"oh, nice!" deep inside...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.72,0:00:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My heart leaps so high\Nthat it pierces the sky!{\i0}	{this sounds cringe as fuck}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.64,0:00:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's past midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.27,0:01:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on, hang on, hang on!\NWhat's wrong with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.98,0:01:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,, I need to study, damnit!\NStudy, study, study!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.70,0:01:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess just stacking samples isn't going to cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.83,0:01:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, maybe I should\Nmake this part a little more subdued...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.22,0:01:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Study!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:36.08,OPStyle,,0,0,0,,This unfinished beat covers the night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.08,0:01:39.00,OPStyle,,0,0,0,,Embracing us before we're crushed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.00,0:01:40.92,OPStyle,,0,0,0,,Even if your hand is unreliable
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.92,0:01:43.71,OPStyle,,0,0,0,,That is your own hand
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.71,0:01:46.55,OPStyle,,0,0,0,,There will be change if you just reach out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.18,0:01:56.31,OPStyle,,0,0,0,,Crying in a crowd with a voiceless voice
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.31,0:02:00.56,OPStyle,,0,0,0,,Come morning, the footsteps drown out the voice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.56,0:02:04.19,OPStyle,,0,0,0,,No matter how much time passes, it never dries
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.19,0:02:09.28,OPStyle,,0,0,0,,The cold, muddy waters of a decaying city
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.28,0:02:10.78,OPStyle,,0,0,0,,In a world where nothing changes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.12,0:02:13.62,OPStyle,,0,0,0,,We have to live through it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.62,0:02:16.91,OPStyle,,0,0,0,,It may be dumb, but we have no choice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.91,0:02:19.58,OPStyle,,0,0,0,,We've already started walking
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:22.84,OPStyle,,0,0,0,,It may seem unreal, it may seem stupid
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:25.63,OPStyle,,0,0,0,,This hopeless city of ours
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.63,0:02:27.92,OPStyle,,0,0,0,,But I still saw it with my own eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.92,0:02:30.80,OPStyle,,0,0,0,,I touched it with these hands, see? See?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:34.10,OPStyle,,0,0,0,,See? There it goes again, it's so stupid
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.10,0:02:36.93,OPStyle,,0,0,0,,Shine a light through the hopeless darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.93,0:02:39.10,OPStyle,,0,0,0,,This isn't a dream, even in a dead city
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.10,0:02:42.90,OPStyle,,0,0,0,,Giving up won't change anything, even now, now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:45.65,OPStyle,,0,0,0,,Now, this unfinished beat covers the night
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.65,0:02:48.49,OPStyle,,0,0,0,,Embracing us before we're crushed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.49,0:02:50.33,OPStyle,,0,0,0,,Even if your hand is unreliable
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.33,0:02:53.24,OPStyle,,0,0,0,,That is your own hand
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.24,0:02:55.91,OPStyle,,0,0,0,,Everything will change if you just reach out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:08.07,MarySigns,,0,0,0,,{\an3}Stupid Q&A
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:08.07,TLnote,,0,0,0,,{\an7}TL note: reference to a song by Eastern Youth https://youtu.be/NL5D6-7C9hg
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The pigeon was on the rhythm...{\i0}		{spoken in English}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.46,0:03:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I haven't even covered two pages since yesterday.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I might as well have just been goofing off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.26,0:03:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, a guitar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.26,0:03:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think this is what\Nthey call an acoustic guitar?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.48,0:03:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Nina-chan! Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you eaten?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We have meat buns! M-e-a-t b-u-n-s!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.28,0:03:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a savage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're such a princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.91,0:03:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You put sauce on your meat buns?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:04:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.33,0:04:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl at my school
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,works in Chinatown and got some leftovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.17,0:04:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.51,0:04:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It tastes great, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- So about that song...\N- Is it done?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.93,0:04:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish it were that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you call us here then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.31,0:04:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I live pretty far away, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.94,0:04:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured we should talk about what sort of song we wanna do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What best suits the three of us? I just can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.49,0:04:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I can drum, that's enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.74,0:04:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Nina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It tastes great, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only been a week since I taught you how to use that app, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.47,0:05:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You came up with this in such a short time? Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.81,0:05:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Momoka-san said
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,that even if I can't read sheet music, I could do it by feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.06,0:05:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I wasn't expecting something this complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You must've spent, like, eight hours every day on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.66,0:05:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.41,0:05:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to study! I have to study!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Called it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.25,0:05:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all your fault for teaching me this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.67,0:05:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it wouldn't impact my studies!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take it out on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.47,0:05:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.93,0:05:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know, then don't blame me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.76,0:05:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.81,0:05:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.31,0:05:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have taught you.\NI'll delete the app, so you just focus on singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't delete it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.48,0:05:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Make up your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.77,0:05:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my own fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.15,0:05:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I should leave band stuff to you,\Nand switch gears when I need to, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.03,0:05:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.45,0:06:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, what's with her? She's loopy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.04,0:06:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.67,0:06:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what about the rest of the meat buns?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have them! Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's walk to the station together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.31,0:06:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Writing a song like that really is incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.65,0:06:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never manage it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.57,0:06:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That was just, you know, monkey see, monkey do...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But the lyrics are a totally different story.		{unclear if she's saying that she couldn't possibly write lyrics or that Nina won't be able to}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.83,0:06:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I'm going to drop by the convenience store...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.67,0:06:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.88,0:07:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, that's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.34,0:07:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to walk home anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta go to work. Is that a no?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, you can go once class is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.79,0:07:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Just take it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.34,0:07:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember the meat buns!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.01,0:07:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is famous...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.89,0:07:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.89,0:07:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What a bumpkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.60,0:07:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.02,0:07:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.15,0:07:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This way?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.57,0:07:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.24,0:08:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.00,0:08:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.84,0:08:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for Awa-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Awa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean Subaru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.89,0:08:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.23,0:08:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we can adlib that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.65,0:08:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.07,0:08:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you manage to get here okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd called the school, I could've come to get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry it took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.24,0:08:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.45,0:08:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.29,0:08:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What, did you lose it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Teehee, silly me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.33,0:08:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, they're calling for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.17,0:09:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- Okay.\N- See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.09,0:09:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy your evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.71,0:09:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you free now? Let's get some dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.88,0:09:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.18,0:09:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I, uh, have to study...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How about on the weekend then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.44,0:09:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, really, it was no trouble.\NI was already in the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.73,0:09:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now if you'll excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.45,0:09:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The band. Should I quit the band?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.41,0:09:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not stupid. I can tell you're avoiding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.46,0:09:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to get in your way or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.34,0:09:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There are other bands out there I could join.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.25,0:09:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, really, it's not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.01,0:09:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.10,0:09:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:09:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:10:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I can study later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all pretty flexible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.28,0:10:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that. I mean me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I only started playing in my club\Nwhen I was in middle school,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,so I can't get too uppity about it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Bands are all about different people making music together,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and it can get pretty crowded.	{better way to translate 濃密? too many cooks spoils the broth?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.50,0:10:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When there's a disagreement, you can't just leave it be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you try and pretend nothing's wrong,\Nthings will inevitably break down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.13,0:10:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you don't like me,\Nyou should just say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I don't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.35,0:10:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a me problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.48,0:10:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired of hearing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.06,0:10:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I'm a bitch. {嫌われがち}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.19,0:10:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, no, that's not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just, I tend to keep my distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.24,0:10:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm shy, and people have to act considerate of me. {気遣われる}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.45,0:10:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I don't like it.	{repetitive phrasing}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But like, I find myself thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.75,0:11:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"I won't fall for that! I'm not that naive!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.63,0:11:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,whenever someone tries to get along with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.42,0:11:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so high maintenance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.92,0:11:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be why you dropped out of high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.26,0:11:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.22,0:11:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, she told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.60,0:11:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be nice up there on your high horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.73,0:11:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now see here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got the wrong idea about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They call it an acting school,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but they don't award high school diplomas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.41,0:11:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the same boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're aiming to become an actress!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.91,0:11:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that mean you're chasing your dream?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell people that with your head held high!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.96,0:11:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, you've got the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.59,0:11:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you recognize her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I might.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Detective Granny's Case Files{\i0}.\NThey air reruns during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.01,0:11:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.93,0:12:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She won't shut up about wanting me\Nto follow in her footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.02,0:12:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'll put in a good word for you,\Nso enrol in this acting school."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So are you going to become an actress?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.57,0:12:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not really aiming to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.99,0:12:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're still attending an acting school...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.95,0:12:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? It drives me crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.08,0:12:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"This isn't what I want. What am I doing here?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.83,0:12:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But no one else sees things the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.58,0:12:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They all just think it's natural, given my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.26,0:12:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what about the band?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.76,0:12:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just my own way of fighting back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Back in middle school, I swore I'd never join the Theatre Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I like music, so I joined the Light Music Club instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.64,0:12:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It was more fun that I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I even secretly started my own band at one point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Your grandmother didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.69,0:12:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, have you seen Hachiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.78,0:12:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't people think we're hicks?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.78,0:12:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares? You {\i1}are{\i0} a hick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:13:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,In for a penny, in for a pound.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.08,0:13:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to start calling you Nina,\Nyou little punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Girls Band Cry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}SUNDAY NOON
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.54,0:13:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A public concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.55,0:13:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. I figured that'd be\Na good way to kick things off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.05,0:13:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already booked a slot at an event on Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.97,0:13:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't we going to record a song and post it online first?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.31,0:13:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do that too,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.10,0:13:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but I just feel like the three of us		{なんかライブって感じがするんだよね、この３人って}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- are like a concert.\N- A concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.65,0:13:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw the photo you sent me the other day,\Nyou two struck me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.19,0:13:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,as having this inescapable sense of misfortune, or dissatisfaction.		{拭えない不幸感っていうか不満が滲み出てる}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- How rude.\N- That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.95,0:13:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's exactly why I reached out to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- What do you think, Nina?\N- It kind of ticks me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.25,0:13:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I kind of get what she means, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.71,0:13:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we even perform without a bassist?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:13:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't play, can you Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:14:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The event is in the city. We'll figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, we have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.22,0:14:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A looper pedal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.93,0:14:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You record some music like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.74,0:14:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And presto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, a public concert means...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd have to sing in front of people, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously. You saw me do it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.25,0:14:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where are you going?\N- Home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.46,0:14:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it a rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.97,0:14:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me! This wasn't what we agreed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.43,0:14:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit complaining! You sang in front of the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the exact same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.72,0:14:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy for you to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.02,0:14:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never done this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. If things go wrong, I'll cover for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.27,0:14:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:14:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're way better than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.82,0:14:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna play the guitar then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.61,0:15:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep telling you,\NI want to hear you sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.28,0:15:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get it once you do it. Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.96,0:15:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.09,0:15:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you quitting the band then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.26,0:15:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I am. It was nice knowing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.68,0:15:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so unfair to take the band hostage like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.53,0:15:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Your argument's falling apart.			{sounds like 議論が破綻しているぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- But I...\N- Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of whether it goes well or not,\Nregardless of whether we flop or fly,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.29,0:15:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you're gonna regret it either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you're like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's...\N- The truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.67,0:15:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You might as well bare it all			{すっ裸になって}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.46,0:15:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and sing with whatever you're feeling right now.		{better way to phrase this?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina got blown the fuck out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.47,0:16:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.05,0:16:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shove that rage into your singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's who you really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, they've got some pretty nice gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.86,0:16:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. They're the cheapest place in the area, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.07,0:16:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give this a go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.58,0:16:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.21,0:16:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, have you memorized the song\NI sent you the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've worked in bits of the song you wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.47,0:16:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool. Try singing, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.18,0:16:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you didn't see this coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all so sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.89,0:16:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, just relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.43,0:16:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just practice. No one expects it to go perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.02,0:16:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if you screw up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.06,0:16:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.58,0:17:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Slower.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.52,0:17:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.66,0:17:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.37,0:17:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got goosebumps!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.54,0:18:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Really crazy goosebumps!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.67,0:18:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.88,0:18:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You've fallen for Momoka-san's trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.42,0:18:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you know how it feels,\Nyou'll never be able to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.30,0:18:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.60,0:18:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Homo sapiens, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.89,0:18:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,are genetically wired to dance to music.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our base instinct to sing and dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.52,0:18:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.48,0:18:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. You just reminded me of how nice your voice is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.90,0:18:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.36,0:18:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You gave me goosebumps, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.66,0:18:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A medium and a beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Medium, no onions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.08,0:18:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Medium.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.38,0:18:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You sound hungover.				{酒明けか}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You both told me to sing as hard as I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but nobody actually sings so hard their voice dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.01,0:18:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.47,0:18:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"Thank yer very much."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.06,0:19:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it'll mend by tomorrow,\Nbut you gotta take care of your throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.39,0:19:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you three in a band?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.06,0:19:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a guitar case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.03,0:19:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome to come see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.53,0:19:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}SHIN-KAWASAKI (TENTATIVE)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.70,0:19:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She invited us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.41,0:19:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We could invite them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe after we see them first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.63,0:19:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.88,0:19:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.34,0:19:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.97,0:19:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She paid for us again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Both here and at karaoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.40,0:19:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's she looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.15,0:19:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably her former bandmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.90,0:19:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.66,0:20:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The next band is making their debut performance today!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.87,0:20:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're a three woman band, started in Kawasaki!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.33,0:20:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Their name is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,"Shin-Kawasaki"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.59,0:20:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to have to discuss our band name later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.47,0:20:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, it's just tentative.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.06,0:20:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.02,0:20:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You plan on going on stage dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.69,0:20:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I not?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.19,0:20:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I did tell you to bare it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.11,0:20:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Go get changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.29,0:20:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ahem. This is a business-related announcement.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.04,0:20:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought the outfit you hated the most would work best.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.54,0:20:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't overthink it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.30,0:20:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just cram in everything you think and feel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.59,0:20:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't worry. Trust me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:20:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're weak, but so stubborn.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.93,0:21:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're cowardly, but so confident.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.31,0:21:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're a bundle of self-contradiction.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.39,0:21:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a compliment!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Nina! It's time to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.53,0:21:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's just how gloomy and pent up you are.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.15,0:21:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that's...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.99,0:21:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well and truly...\NRock.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.66,0:21:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No one here knows you.\NNo one here cares.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.93,0:21:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that's what makes things interesting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:22:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so rock'n'roll, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.54,0:22:06.29,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,If nothing changes\NNo matter how long I wait
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.46,0:22:09.67,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,Then there's nobody I can rely on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.83,0:22:14.51,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,It's not as if the pain disappears\NWhen you blame someone else
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.67,0:22:17.26,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,I pray to say goodbye\NTo cowering every day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.43,0:22:19.59,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,Holding my knees to my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:24.14,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,I don't even believe in God
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.31,0:22:29.15,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,Shut up\N(Shut up)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.44,0:22:34.78,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone\N(Leave me alone)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.94,0:22:37.36,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,A stranger sings\NUntil they lose their voice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.53,0:22:39.82,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,Telling me that I'm not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.99,0:22:43.83,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that to some people\NThose words are enough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.24,0:22:45.87,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.04,0:22:47.21,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.37,0:22:48.33,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,Was that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.50,0:22:49.67,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,I forgot
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.83,0:22:50.83,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,It's all a pain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.00,0:22:52.13,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,I want to break it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.29,0:22:54.13,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,I don't have the courage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.30,0:22:59.76,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,Someone hurry up and teach me\NA reason to live
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.93,0:23:03.97,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,There are so many people to take my place
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.22,0:23:09.35,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,You can't just tell me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.52,0:23:12.27,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,Take it back if it can be granted
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.44,0:23:14.98,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,I can dream all I want\NThere's still reality
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.15,0:23:17.44,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,Is anyone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.71,0:23:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That...was so...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.01,0:23:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}rock.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.14,0:23:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}AWA SUBARU\NSorry, I'm quitting the band!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.43,0:23:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode:\N"Thanks (Surprise)".
